      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in wonderful shape, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a solid, well-cared-for car without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and has been super well-loved! I\u2019ve really enjoyed every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it just as much. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more!",
      "price": 28900.0,
