    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis exemplifies Japanese engineering of the golden era, powered by the 1.3L 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. The powerplant delivers a seamless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos, providing a linear torque curve through a precise 5-speed manual gearbox. It features a factory Torsen limited-slip differential and a rigid double-wishbone suspension geometry that ensures exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Recent service includes a full cooling system overhaul with a high-capacity aluminum radiator and a simplified vacuum manifold to ensure thermal efficiency. Compression pulses remain strong and consistent. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals are sorted, making this a quintessential driver\u2019s specimen.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
