    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium infotainment system, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. With plenty of tread left on the tires and a firm, quiet ride, this car is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
